com.xekri.leakvm.sdk.keystore

Class KeystoreExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xekri.leakvm.sdk.keystore.KeystoreExtractor

  • public final class KeystoreExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
    KeystoreExtractor class is an useful utility to extract public keys, certificate, certificate chains and ciphers fom the KeyStore
